OL,6,FA fraudster who exploited and
OL,7,Fdefrauded a vulnerable elderly couple
OL,8,Fhe made friends with has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor five and a half years.
OL,11,FPervical Harris, 59, from Mabe
OL,12,FBurnthouse, was sentenced for two
OL,13,Fcounts of fraud, two counts of forgery
OL,14,Fand one count of conspiracy to pervert
OL,15,Fthe course of justice at Truro Crown
OL,16,FCourt on Thursday 12 September.
