OL,6,FThe court heard how the victims had
OL,7,Fcreated wills through a solicitor in
OL,8,F2015, naming Harris as one of the
OL,9,Fexecutors and leaving a small portion
OL,10,Fof their estate to him.
OL,12,FFollowing their deaths in 2017 and
OL,13,F2018, their family became aware of
OL,14,Fsome discrepancies in the wills and
OL,15,Fnoticed that the dates didn't match.
OL,17,FThey tried to get hold of Harris, but
OL,18,Fwhen they couldn't, they contacted
OL,19,Fpolice to report their concerns.
