OL,6,FPolice found that Harris had created
OL,7,Famended wills for the victims in 2016,
OL,8,Fleaving the majority of their estates
OL,9,Fto himself.
OL,11,FHe had also enlisted two vulnerable
OL,12,Flocal men to witness the new
OL,13,Fdocuments, paying them a small amount
OL,14,Fof cash.
OL,16,FHarris pleaded not guilty to the
OL,17,Foffences but was found guilty to five
OL,18,Fcounts in July 2024 by a jury
OL,19,Ffollowing trial.
