OL,6,FInvestigating Officer, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Isabelle Woodall said: "A
OL,8,Ffive-year investigation has concluded
OL,9,Ftoday with the sentencing of a man who
OL,10,Fwas prepared to exploit the most
OL,11,Fvulnerable in society for his own
OL,12,Ffinancial gain.
OL,14,F"The victims in this case had no
OL,15,Fchildren and lived remotely, had no
OL,16,Fway of knowing that the man that they
OL,17,Fbelieved to be a devoted friend, was
OL,18,Fmotivated by greed.
