OL,6,F"The victims' families are private
OL,7,Fpeople who have found the publicity
OL,8,Fsurrounding this case distressing.
OL,9,FTheir patience and unwavering support
OL,10,Fhas been commendable.
OL,12,F"It is with sincere thanks to the
OL,13,Ffamily, including Mr Alan Tucker who
OL,14,Fsadly didn't live to see the
OL,15,Fconclusion, that this matter has come
OL,16,Fto light so it may raise awareness and
OL,17,Fthe profile of this exploitative
OL,18,Fcrime."
